CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 13, 1958, pg. A14 reads: "Guild Check - Mrs. Ann C. Waters, president of the Urban League Guild, presents a check to Richard Evarts, member of the Pittsburgh Urban League board of directors, at the Christmas luncheon held at the Press Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ann C. Waters, president of the Urban League Guild, handing check to Richard Evarts, member of the Pittsburgh Urban League board of directors, standing behind banquet table at Press Club for Christmas luncheon
